import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    airports_by_country = data.groupby('country').size().reset_index(name='counts')
    airports_by_country = airports_by_country.sort_values(by='counts', ascending=False)
    plt.bar(airports_by_country['country'], airports_by_country['counts'])
    plt.title('What is the distribution of airports by country?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    state_counts = data['state'].value_counts()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax.bar(state_counts.index, state_counts.values)
    ax.set_xlabel('State')
    ax.set_ylabel('Number of Airports')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of airports by state?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.hist(data['latitude'], bins=50, color='blue', alpha=0.5)
    ax.axvline(data['latitude'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['latitude'].mean():.2f}")
    ax.axvline(data['latitude'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['latitude'].median():.2f}")
    ax.set_xlabel('Latitude')
    ax.set_ylabel('Frequency')
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of airports by latitude?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
from wordcloud import WordCloud

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    airport_names = ' '.join(data['name'].tolist())
    wordcloud = WordCloud(width = 800, height = 800, 
                background_color ='white', 
                min_font_size = 10).generate(airport_names)
    plt.figure(figsize = (8, 8), facecolor = None) 
    plt.imshow(wordcloud) 
    plt.axis("off") 
    plt.tight_layout(pad = 0) 
    plt.title('What is the distribution of airport names?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
